%H A221443 <a href="/index/Rec#order_09">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (17,168,464,442,30,-88,0,-9,1).
%F A221443 Empirical: a(n) = 17*a(n-1) +168*a(n-2) +464*a(n-3) +442*a(n-4) +30*a(n-5) -88*a(n-6) -9*a(n-8) +a(n-9).
%F A221443 From _Andrew Howroyd_, Jul 16 2026: (Start)
%F A221443 The above empirical formula confirmed using the transfer matrix method.
%F A221443 G.f.: x*(17 + 140*x + 444*x^2 + 516*x^3 - 574*x^4 - 1628*x^5 - 412*x^6 - 52*x^7 + 13*x^8)/((1 + x)*(1 + 2*x - x^2)*(1 - 20*x - 109*x^2 - 116*x^3 - 5*x^4 - 8*x^5 + x^6)). (End)
